ISLAMABAD, Sep 19 (APP): The Election Commission of Pakistan (ECP) on Thursday denied a news item about filing of a miscellaneous petition in the Supreme Court.
“The ECP has not yet taken any decision about filing of a miscellaneous petition in the Supreme Court,” an ECP press release said. “This is complete disinformation,” it added.
